03E\nI\u0027m sure someone could put tracks and a turret on it\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-24T21:23:42Z\u0022 title=\u002206/24/2016 09:23  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 24, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by DoctorDavinci\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Optimist","CreatedById":151904,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-26T01:22:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMinecraft profile pictures make me cringe\u00A0\u250C(\u02F5\u0F0E\u0EB6 \u00A0\u0644\u035F \u00A0\u0F0E\u0EB6\u02F5)\u2510\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E could read the submissions guide?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-26T01:23:28Z\u0022 title=\u002206/26/2016 01:23  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 26, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by The Optimist\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GraviTykillz","CreatedById":60694,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-26T04:40:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://img1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100314182111/cnc/images/f/f7/Nod_Vehicle_-_Scorpion_Tank_0.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022Nod_Vehicle_-_Scorpion_Tank_0.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mordecai_Ender","CreatedById":159156,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-26T20:33:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsomething like Gravitykillz\u0027s comment\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cunjo Carl","CreatedById":162109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T05:52:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt took very little deliberation to embark on the quest to build the worlds greatest (*cough* only) KSP Scorpion tank. It\u0027s with great pleasure that I unveil:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:28px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027trebuchet ms\u0027, helvetica, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EScorpion Tank\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/pgfXvZzhWL8?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159156-mordecai_ender/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022159156\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/159156-mordecai_ender/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Mordecai_Ender\u003C/a\u003E for the challenge! It was unique, required some interesting design considerations, and was hilariously entertaining to pilot. The craft file is happily available upon request, and yes it is as fun to drive as it looks. Cheers!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wibou7","CreatedById":155221,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T18:33:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162109-cunjo-carl/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022162109\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/162109-cunjo-carl/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Cunjo Carl\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E This was awesome!\u00A0 Have some reps.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EgoReaper Jr","CreatedById":166017,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-30T01:32:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/vQeUcSKaAFg?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mordecai_Ender","CreatedById":159156,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-08T17:34:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThese are awesome design but \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162109-cunjo-carl/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022162109\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/162109-cunjo-carl/\u0022 rel=\u0022external\u0022\u003E@Cunjo Carl\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0you could focus on ading BDarmory wepaon it was a requirement and \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/166017-egoreaper-jr/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022166017\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/166017-egoreaper-jr/\u0022 rel=\u0022external\u0022\u003E@EgoReaper Jr\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0if you could add a turret turn mechanism with infernal robotics and a canon like the howitzer it would be awesome\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-08T17:35:05Z\u0022 title=\u002207/08/2016 05:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 8, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Mordecai_Ender\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cunjo Carl","CreatedById":162109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-10T05:59:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBDarmory was a requirement? Oh, typically part mods stated without context infer optional mods not mandatory ones. You might just toss the word \u0027required\u0027 in front of the mods for any others wandering in. I likely won\u0027t be continuing in this challenge using the mods just from a personal preference for stock parts. I enjoy the creative challenge required to accomplish a goal with the limited options. There\u0027s a ton of joy to be found in playing with the wild and interesting parts found in mods too, it\u0027s just not my thing at the moment. You gotta admit, even after the great exhaust damage reduction of v1.1 those stock vectors just tore through the fuel tanks! It still makes me giggle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d be happy to share the ship file if you were interested in grafting some cannons on it? It can laugh off the recoil of two full-blast vectors, which is pretty insanely heavy! Cheers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cunjo Carl","CreatedById":162109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-10T20:27:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/166017-egoreaper-jr/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022166017\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/166017-egoreaper-jr/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@EgoReaper Jr\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0 I was just rewatching your video when I noticed it was your first post in the forums. Welcome! Sweet video- I love the style. Dry bearings are a pain, aren\u0027t they. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}